{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And do you know why the boys were hung?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why they what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look, when, when I met Goldie, if, if we were together for 15 minutes, it was the most.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I-- it was more dangerous, in a way, for me, because I went into the ghetto, but I also had to get out of the ghetto and back to that hotel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he didn't want me, you know, to hang around too long, because he wanted me to get back into safety.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, nobody was walking around in Theresienstadt in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was pretty obvious when, when I was walking from the Jewish part into the-- into the German hotel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It, it wasn't very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- we never-- it wasn't nice meetings, happy meeting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were under so, so much pressure and under so much fear always.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did you see in Theresienstadt?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it was a-- as I said, a Garrison town where they were before soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and now they were- they were Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were Czech people living in, in little houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, if you-- if you wouldn't have known, there was nothing abnormal to see at, at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The street that, that went, that was like a normal road if you today go into some village or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What I knew is what-- that they didn't have much to eat, that, that they cut their hair, and that they had to work very hard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were all young guys, and they didn't mind, because they didn't think-- that was OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were two hours from Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, that didn't seem so dramatic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK, they didn't have the freedom, but they were alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
